# Base URL of the ClevScaffold API, reachable FROM THE DEVICE. A phone or
# emulator cannot resolve your dev machine's "localhost" — use the LAN IP
# (e.g. http://192.168.1.20:3000) or the Android-emulator host alias
# http://10.0.2.2:3000. Expo inlines EXPO_PUBLIC_* vars at bundle time.
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.20:3000
